  "title": "CAT CARE & SERVICE CREW",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>To manage & oversee overall F&B operation & inventories</li><li>To upkeep cafe housekeeping, general cleanliness and hygiene</li><li>To assist in taking care of cafe cats including grooming, feeding & cleaning</li><li>To assist in customer service & orientation</li><li>To assist in preparing, serving of food/beverages & cashiering</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties required</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Comfortable with cats & able to recognize cat’s behaviour & handling practices</li><li>Committed, responsible & well-spoken individual</li><li>Proactive & detail-oriented</li><li>Service-oriented, self-motivated & a good team player</li><li>Must be comfortable meeting & interacting with people</li><li>Willing to learn & pick up new skills for self-development</li><li>Able to work 6 days weekly including weekends & public holidays</li><li>Candidates to have at least 1 year of working experiences in vet clinics, animal shelters, cats or F&B related environment</li><li>Food Hygiene Cert or barista/coffee skills is a bonus</li></ul>",
